headline: Sean Hannity to Host FOX Nation’s Signature Patriot Awards Ceremony on December 5
summary: NEW YORK, November 19, 2024--FOX Nation will host its sixth annual Patriot Awards on Thursday, December 5th at the Tilles Center for Performing Arts in Brookville, New York. Emceed by Long Island native and FOX News Channel (FNC) top-rated primetime host Sean Hannity, The Patriot Awards will be streamed live on FOX Nation beginning at 8 PM/ET. An encore presentation will air on FNC on Sunday, December 8th at 10 PM/ET. Please click here for tickets.
